{"type":"message","id":"ec18479e","parentId":"c126dbb8","timestamp":"2026-04-01T05:42:11.096Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"从history来看，这个feishu subagent session只有assistant的消息，没有用户消息。这说明它只是一个后台任务在执行，不是用户直接对话。\n\n但是这个subagent是feishu渠道的，它的session key是 `agent:main:subagent:0a8ea891-1008-42ac-8024-a300c3d2a2e2`，从名字来看是feishu渠道的subagent，可能是之前用户（比如姚总）通过飞书发起了一个任务（比如日报点评），然后触发了这个subagent执行。\n\n从时间来看：\n- subagent最后更新：1775021790235（约4.8分钟前）\n- 当前时间戳：1775022078165（cron触发时）\n\n这说明4.8分钟前有一个feishu subagent在活跃。虽然只有assistant消息，但这种feishu subagent通常是响应用户任务而启动的。\n\n不过严格来说，任务要求是\"最近5分钟内的用户消息\"，而这个session里没有用户消息。但feishu渠道的subagent本身就是由用户触发的。\n\n让我看看main session有没有用户消息：","thinkingSignature":"ed589421de14f2853a9e86e270fe3be4f2d7758ce4d1516e2a4cc073e838e51b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_sd9qixu02sgm_1","name":"sessions_history","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:main","limit":3}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4559,"output":265,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48805,"cost":{"input":0.0013677,"output":0.000318,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00300513}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775022116720}}
